TITLE: Integrating TanStack Form with TanStack Query in Vue.js
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to use TanStack Query to fetch asynchronous data for initializing a TanStack Form in Vue.js. It handles loading states by showing a loading indicator while data is being fetched and then uses the fetched data as default values for the form. The form uses reactive values that update when the query data changes.
