SOURCE: https://github.com/tanstack/form/blob/main/docs/reference/type-aliases/deepkeys.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
type DeepKeys<T> = unknown extends T ? string : DeepKeysAndValues<T>["key"];
```

